  ('retired-10ced7e2-moex-00265', 'retired-10ced7e2', 'retired-10ced7e2-moex-110-b96fcbef', 'sub-retired-10ced7e2-09', NULL, 'essay', '17 歲之甲未得其父母（乙、丙）同意下，將其所有之遊戲機（市價 4萬
